{"id":146202,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：药家鑫案将在周五宣判/","date":"2011-04-21T01:33:12Z","modified":"2012-02-16T22:50:27Z","title":"简讯：药家鑫案将在周五宣判","content":"<div>\n<p>开车撞人后将持刀将受伤者刺死的西安大学生药家鑫将在周五（22日）被一审宣判。</p>\n<p>药家鑫案在中国引起广泛的社会关注。</p>\n<p>他在撞伤农民工张妙后，因担心对方索要巨额赔偿，而持刀行凶。</p>\n<p>药家鑫被控故意杀人罪，最高可能被判处死刑。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/UtHHaA0z8ioGAqgBVBe7Iu5FBI8/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/UtHHaA0z8ioGAqgBVBe7Iu5FBI8/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/UtHHaA0z8ioGAqgBVBe7Iu5FBI8/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/UtHHaA0z8ioGAqgBVBe7Iu5FBI8/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/giihKSZBebk\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=752465\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[15908]}